76561198038892067,Recommended,249230,13619708,"Posted: 26 December, 2014",all,kaay,"Risen 3 offers great entertainment value. It was designed to be fun and enjoyable to play for a more casual gamer, or a gamer that enjoys some pleasant and relaxed gameplay once in a while.What sets this game apart from other action-rpgs is the beautiful handcrafted world that is a joy to explore, no other developer can compete with Piranha Bytes in this respect.The game offers a light-hearted story that is well told, and a lot of side quests.You eventually get a good ship and start building your crew of companions, each with their own stories, personalities and side quests.The assortment of skills and spells is very nice and varies somewhat depending on what faction you chose to join.The character progression is fairly fast compared to previous games.The one thing that is most important about the combat is to NOT tap the attack button repeatedly. Tap once, wait for the move to reach its peak then tap again, with a bit of practice you will get the timing which is very forgiving. You can also tap by listening to the sound. The dodge move has 100% invincibility window, making it very efficient when you want to get away from a tough spot.If you are looking for pleasant gameplay and good entertainment this is the best game you can get."
