76561197972336905,Not Recommended,249230,34698541,Posted: 2 September,all,darrensinbox,"Too bad because this game does have some decent RPG progression, acceptable graphics, and though corny, voice acted.Two things ended up being give-up show-stoppers for me...First, for a combat heavy game, combat just isn't much fun.  The game seems to want you to block a few times and let your companion tank, which is fine, but in total it just feels slow, boring, repetative, and random.  At least mobs don't respawn.Second, there is a significant game bug that causes the game to place your character in limbo after the semi-lengthy sea battles.  Others have suggested some possible work-arounds, but as far as I can tell it's just random.  If it happens, re-load, replay the same battle, hope the game doesn't hang in this way.May try again later, but gave up on this title for now."
